study_pop.textblock:
ICU patients treated in Stockholm between 2007 and 2017 in the following five ICUs from
three hospitals: Karolinska University Hospital in Solna - central medico-surgical ICU;
Karolinska University Hospital in Solna - cardiothoracic ICU; Karolinska University
Hospital Huddinge - medico-surgical ICU; Södersjukhuset Hospital - medical ICU;
Södersjukhuset Hospital - surgical ICU.
